{"tid":1853801,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"口罩危機：誠哥諗諗投資我嘅設計","createTime":"2020-01-31T07:17:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-14T10:29:22.000Z","uid":271365,"like":15,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"a2be2444e8fca27cd820172299586acfddaf503e","tid":1853801,"uid":271365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T07:17:30.000Z","msg":"南韓多年前有一齣電影《流感》<br />\n講述一批南亞人經香港偷渡到南韓做黑工<br />\n偷渡客中有人疑感染新型流感<br />\n結果成班偷渡客响途中相繼染病，死剩一人<br />\n病毒結果超速在南韓社區擴散⋯<br />\n<br />\n重點唔係呢套戲嘅內容（有點誇張嘅）<br />\n而係當中出現過嘅非一次性「口罩」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M4TCOsT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM4TCOsT.png&h=1e84fc49&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n圖片中可見口罩有兩種造形<br />\n分別在於濾芯設計<br />\n一款係比較小巧，另一款就應該功能好啲<br />\n我唔知現實有無咁嘅口罩<br />\n如果有大家可能唔洗周圍撲罩撲得咁辛苦<br />\n無嘅話，咁我就諗咗一晚，按照南韓套戲嘅口罩呼吸器<br />\n做咗個咁嘅設計<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vArkRg3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvArkRg3.jpg&h=122de494&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我暫且叫佢做未來口罩（呼吸器） Future Respirator<br />\n成個呼吸器由幾個組件合成<br />\n可以獨立更換<br />\n方便更換用作過濾細菌病毒嘅消毒劑同濾膜<br />\n<br />\n殺菌消毒嘅原理<br />\n包括採用了純銅可以殺病毒細菌嘅特性<br />\n而細銅管可以增加細菌毒接觸到銅嘅機會<br />\n同時亦可以令到進入消毒液體嘅氣泡大細<br />\n兩者希望都可以提高殺菌殺毒嘅功效<br />\n因為消毒液體總會有氣味<br />\n所以增加了好似現時一般外科口罩嘅濾層設計<br />\n除咗減除氣味之餘<br />\n亦可以過濾在前面利用細銅管同消毒劑兩層機制嘅漏網病毒細菌<br />\n吸入口同呼氣口都有活門只可以入氣或出氣<br />\n防止氣體回流<br />\n<br />\n利申：非任何工程師，以上諗法純粹憑空想像，唔知係咪可行<br />\n更加唔敢亂講個殺毒滅菌功效有幾大<br />\n如果真係有投資者願意開發<br />\n我作為一個地球人向呢位投資者致敬"},{"pid":"c49d14bb56c8c8d67893f37f4a3abe8dcde6d43e","tid":1853801,"uid":212274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T07:18:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e41975fece9adbcc746fbc25d210683a85668a9","tid":1853801,"uid":17641,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T07:20:08.000Z","msg":"老衲想投資100億<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87da25de82f38da0b170d78783405773c13f1219","tid":1853801,"uid":321618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T07:20:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">抗疫不忘抗爭</span></span><br />\n希望大家幫p牌推推<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n解答到 國際關係 海洋法庭制裁警暴<br />\n呢啲議題 <br />\n唔好比肺炎spin開左 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">我地仲未光復到香港！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">一齊收港共支共皮</span><br />\n<br />\n沈旭暉高汁分析 點光復香港<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1853544\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1853544</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5442793d0491b9de8d8a6b9d2dacf27ac945a7d7","tid":1853801,"uid":193642,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T07:21:01.000Z","msg":"吸消毒液體會變慢性中毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea465f30918d421c2bb32dadfb38d3ea5311907a","tid":1853801,"uid":271365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e41975fece9adbcc746fbc25d210683a85668a9","tid":1853801,"uid":17641,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T07:20:08.000Z","msg":"老衲想投資100億<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T07:22:11.000Z","msg":"大師，我唔識開廠，無咁嘅人脈<br />\n你有一百億，請自行搵人進行，謝謝<br />\n（我無要求任何回報）"},{"pid":"a9df9c58696698b9e7f157e0b5585cb84d181418","tid":1853801,"uid":82722,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T07:22:35.000Z","msg":"消毒液係咪用酒精<br />\n消毒液好多都揮發性<br />\n咁樣吸法好快中毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2baeebddb58af08cf8a6475ca573cba0c14c022d","tid":1853801,"uid":154106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e41975fece9adbcc746fbc25d210683a85668a9","tid":1853801,"uid":17641,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T07:20:08.000Z","msg":"老衲想投資100億<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T07:22:53.000Z","msg":"一百億精蟲？"},{"pid":"a481ca384c62e50ee238578101234a9af204f7e1","tid":1853801,"uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T07:22:55.000Z","msg":"即係豬咀加強版，暫時用住豬咀先"},{"pid":"242d097f43b59cb648b9ae3b14e157bdfc5eb344","tid":1853801,"uid":111105,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T07:23:23.000Z","msg":"點解唔要現成既豬嘴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91627d681290d998490c42ea4bfc0bd5bdb3c0c0","tid":1853801,"uid":271365,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5442793d0491b9de8d8a6b9d2dacf27ac945a7d7","tid":1853801,"uid":193642,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T07:21:01.000Z","msg":"吸消毒液體會變慢性中毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T07:23:38.000Z","msg":"都有咁嘅可能<br />\n呢個真係要搵專家研究<br />\n其實最初諗嘅殺毒劑只係75%酒精<br />\n但係驚話用酒精會聞到醉咗⋯"},{"pid":"1e19d56e6e95d94e3879dbe84c35a595c5cca1c6","tid":1853801,"uid":147803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T07:24:02.000Z","msg":"液體<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29ca5ab83fb5bf84248d72cb3d64f27523d2ea50","tid":1853801,"uid":40171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T07:25:30.000Z","msg":"個設計咁似核反應堆 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae5f09527f20bb40c79a0bf1b9ac600aebc47b13","tid":1853801,"uid":283222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T07:27:59.000Z","msg":"燒酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69d1960b278c49771cfee77412dbf73c5e402dff","tid":1853801,"uid":271365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"242d097f43b59cb648b9ae3b14e157bdfc5eb344","tid":